events.name: Illinois Fighting Illini at Wisconsin Badgers

headlines.description: — Wisconsin will try to get back on track against Illinois on Saturday after suffering consecutive losses for just the fifth time in seven seasons under coach Paul Chryst.
headlines.shortLinkText: Struggling Wisconsin looks to bounce back against Illinois
